<h2><strong>Using in Cooking and Seasoning</strong></h2>
<p data-dmc="section">ShivalikÂ salt is an alternative to table salt. The crystals of the salt are best added to soups, stews or marinades, where they are easily dissolved.</p>

<h2 class="header"><strong><span data-dmc="section-headline">Using in Brine Therapy</span></strong></h2>
